      <h1 class="mb-4">About Weather Forecast</h1>
      
      <p class="lead mb-4">
        Weather Forecast is a modern weather application designed to provide accurate and up-to-date weather information for locations around the world.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Features</h2>
      <ul class="mb-4">
        <li>Current weather conditions with detailed metrics</li>
        <li>5-day and 7-day weather forecasts</li>
        <li>Interactive weather maps with multiple layers</li>
        <li>Temperature and precipitation trend charts</li>
        <li>Latest weather news and updates</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Data Sources</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Weather Forecast uses data from the following sources:
      </p>
      <ul class="mb-4">
        <li><strong>OpenWeatherMap API</strong> - For weather data, forecasts, and map layers</li>
        <li><strong>New York Times API</strong> - For weather-related news and articles</li>
      </ul>
      
