      <h2 class="h4 mb-3">How It Works</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Weather Forecast uses the OpenWeatherMap API to fetch current weather conditions and forecast data for any location worldwide. 
        The application processes this data and presents it in an easy-to-understand format with visual elements like charts and maps.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        The interactive weather maps use Leaflet.js with OpenWeatherMap map layers to display various weather conditions such as temperature, 
        precipitation, clouds, wind, and pressure. The forecast charts are created using Chart.js to visualize temperature trends and 
        precipitation probabilities over time.
      </p>
      
